Young Master Yi is no longer in Tianqi.

597
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:37,900
He sold the business to our current boss.

598
00:38:37,900 --> 00:38:41,000
Then, do you know where he is now?

599
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:42,900
I don't know.

