624
00:40:14,200 --> 00:40:17,100
I'll let you handle it then.

625
00:40:17,100 --> 00:40:18,700
Yes, Supervisor.

626
00:40:21,800 --> 00:40:24,200
Why exactly did you come outside?

627
00:40:24,200 --> 00:40:26,600
It's not to have fun, right?

628
00:40:26,600 --> 00:40:28,300
What do you know?

